shortDescription: You will need to meet the convoy at the rendezvous point, re-group, and get to the target landing zone. After that, our dropship will pick up the convoy while you will have to move on your own towards the Steiner controlled territory.
longDescription: You need to act fast on this one. If you wait too long, you will be overwhelmed by Falcon's forces.

dialogueContent.words: Commander, the Gray Death Legion convoy is right on schedule, and as predicted, we're picking up Falcon's units in the area.
Move to intercept the convoy and provide cover and support while they escape.
Once they're safely away, you need to make a run towards Steiner controlled territory.
Excellent work, Commander. You have successfully reached Steiner territory.
That's the whole convoy down, Commander. Damn! I'm scrubbing the mission.
Commander. The enemy had deployed reinforcements and they are inbound. Expect increased resistance.
More contacts on the sensors, Commander. Looks like Falcons are closing on your position.
You've reached the extraction point for the objective vehicles. Hold there are keep them safe until we can get them out.
Signal from the Gray Death Legion convoy leader, Commander. They're headed to the extraction point now. Keep them alive!
Keep in mind that the convoy will try to stay near you for protection. Continue advancing to get them to the extract point!
And they are away! The convoy is safely out of the AO. Good work, Commander. Now get your remaining forces to Steiner territory.
